<%
meta title: "Left Coast Search | Candidates",
     description: "Left Coast Search understands making a change in your career
      is a big step. We are here to help you every step of the way!"
%>
<div id="candidate-header">
  <div class="carousel-inner">
    <%= image_tag("https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/leftcoastsearch/candidate-header.jpg") %>
    <div class="carousel-caption">
      <div id="candidate-header-text">
        YOUR LAST JOB SEARCH
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="universal-page" id="candidate-page">
  <div>
    <h1><b>Our Promise</b></h1>
    At Left Coast Search, we connect great people with great companies by completing a thorough
    interview process with every candidate we meet to ensure the right fit. Left
    Coast Search understands making a change in your career is a big step.
    We are here to help you every step of the way. We will keep your search completely
    confidential and our team will speak with you about each opportunity before submitting your resume to our client.
  </div>
  <hr>
  <div>
  <h2>Services</h2>
    Left Coast Search offers resume review, interview coaching, networking opportunities and salary review.
    We offer career assistance and placements in various industries. We place skilled
    accounting, finance, human resources and administrative professionals.
  </div>
  <br>
  <div>
    We work diligently to offer a valuable, friendly, personal approach to assist
    you during the interview process. Interviewing can be stressful. Our job is to
    take the stress out of this process by offering a one of a kind experience through
    great customer service and communication. Our number one priority is finding you the right match.
  </div>
  <br>
  <div>
    For our temporary employees, we offer complete benefit packages, easy to use online
    payroll and timekeeping systems, job opportunities with top companies, resume review,
    interview coaching and great customer service.
  </div>
  <br>
  <div>
  <h2>Let's Get Started!</div>
    If you're in the market for a new position, please head over to our <%= link_to "Job Board", jobs_path %>
    to see a full list of our exciting positions. If you don't see the right fit,
    <%= link_to "send us your resume", new_resume_path %> and we'll keep you in mind
    for future opportunities!
  </div>
</div>
